---
title: Cal Smart Thai-Style Pork Salad with Peanut Soy Dressing
description: Unlock the powerful flavour of peanuts with tonight's Cal Smart Thai-Style Pork Salad! Filled with fresh vegetable, juicy pork chops and all covered with a truly flavour-packed peanut sauce, this salad could be you new Cal Smart go-to!

